# Authentication Module — AI Farmer Companion (v2 Architecture)

This document presents the updated architecture for the Authentication Module, incorporating significant design improvements for a production-grade, microservices-ready modular monolith.

## 1. High-Level Design (HLD)

### 1.1 System Context

The AI Farmer Companion backend follows a Modular Monolith architecture, preparing for an eventual migration to microservices. The Authentication module provides the security boundary for the entire application.

